{"tid":2499604,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以分辨定義目的同意義","createTime":"2021-04-22T04:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T06:50:50.000Z","uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87c333fc8a49515a432a28bae264bf55808b6f54","tid":2499604,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"我返工，為揾食，揾食算係目的定意義<br />\n意義係揾食，令到自己「好似過得好咗」算唔算意義<br />\n定係意義要深層次啲嘅，係非物質上嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d95bb329dbadcee25f862b22822256c1a9d317b","tid":2499604,"uid":380245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"a04470827590a950b0e43a7961ee079844f6747b","tid":2499604,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"目的可以和價值無關（例如為世所迫、生活迫人），<br />\n但意義是符合自己的價值觀的，<br />\n除非某人的價值觀就是生存/搵錢，那就真的是在你的問題中目的=意義了。"}]}